 # 🤖 EmotiBot: A GenAI-Powered Mental Health Chat Companion

**EmotiBot** is an empathetic, conversational AI designed to support users through mental health challenges, casual emotional check-ins, or just a friendly chat. Powered by **LangGraph**, **Gemini 2.0 Flash**, and integrated with **LangChain tools**, EmotiBot delivers human-like, emotionally intelligent conversations tailored to the user’s emotional state.

### Set up your API key

If you don't already have an API key, you can grab one from [AI Studio](https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey). You can find [detailed instructions in the docs](https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/api-key).


---

## 🌟 Features

- 🧠 Emotion-aware conversation powered by Large Language Models (LLMs)
- 💬 Real-time, interactive chat interface
- 📊 Emotion classification & response personalization
- ⚙️ Built using LangGraph on top of Gemini 2.0 Flash
- 📦 Deployed in a professional UI with ipywidgets (for Kaggle Notebooks)

 You can also check it on [kaggle](https://www.kaggle.com/code/aniketmaind/emotibot-where-emotional-intelligence-meets-genai).
